com.google.appinventor.shared.rpc
Class ServerLayout

java.lang.Object
  com.google.appinventor.shared.rpc.ServerLayout

public class ServerLayout
extends Object

Configuration of the URL namespace on the ODE server. Note that this must match the paths defined in the war/WEB-INF/web.xml file.
